quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  2,154,"“Ndipo musanene za amene aphedwa pa njira ya Allah kuti: “Ngakufa.” Iyayi ngamoyo, koma inu simuzindikira"
  2,155,"“Ndipo ndithu tikuyesani ndi chinachake monga mantha, njala, kuchepa kwa chuma, kutaika kwa miyoyo ndi kuonongeka kwa mbeu. Tero auze nkhani yabwino opirira"
  2,156,"“Omwe vuto lililonse likawapeza amati: “Ndithudi, ife nga Allah, ndipo ndithu kwa Iye tidzabwerera.”"
  2,157,“Otero ndi amene pa iwo pali madalitso ochokera kwa Mbuye wawo ndi chifundo. Ndiponso iwo ndi amene ali oongoka
  2,158,"“Ndithudi, Safaa ndi Marwa ndizizindikiro zolemekezera chipembedzo cha Allah. Choncho, amene akukachita mapemphero a Hajj ku nyumbayo, kapena kuchita Umrah, sikulakwa kwa iye kuzungulira pamenepo (pakati pamapiri amenewo). Ndipo amene achite chabwino modzipereka (adzalipidwa). Ndithudi Allah Ngothokoza; Ngodziwa"
  2,159,"“Ndithudi, amene akubisa zimene tavumbulutsa zomwe ndi zisonyezo zoonekera poyera, ndi chiongoko pambuyo pozifotokoza mwatsatanetsatane kwa anthu m’Buku, Allah akuwatembelera iwo. Ndiponso akuwatembelera otembelera"
  2,160,"“Kupatula amene alapa ndi kukonza (zolakwika) nachilongosola (choonadicho kwa anthu), iwowo ndi amene ndiwalandira kulapa kwao. Ndipo ine Ngolandira kulapa kwambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"
  2,161,"“Ndithudi, arnene sadakhulupirire, namwalira ali osakhulupirira, pa iwo pali matembelero a Allah, angelo ndi anthu onse"
  2,162,"“M’menemo (m’chilango cha matembelero) adzakhalamo nthawi yaitali. Ndipo chilango sichidzapeputsidwa kwa iwo, ndipo sadzapatsidwa nthawi (yopumula)"
  2,163,"“Ndipo mulungu wanu ndi Mulungu mmodzi basi. Palibe wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye. Ngwachifundo chambiri, Ngwachisoni chosatha"